Same Time. Her books are translated into thirty-two languages. In 2001 she was awarded the Jerusalem Prize for her body of work, and in 2003 she received the Prince of Asturias Prize for Literature and the Peace Prize of the German Book Trade. She died in December 2004.","summary":"‘An exemplary demonstration of the power of the intellect in the face of the lethal metaphors of fear’\nMichael Ignatieff, New Republic\n‘Whatever Sontag writes is passionate…hers is the satirist’s pity for our ignorance and folly’\nJonathan Keates, Observer\n《疾病的隐喻》一书收录了桑塔格两篇重要论文《作为隐喻的疾病》及《艾滋病及其隐喻》，在文章中桑塔格反思并批判了诸如结核病、艾滋病、癌症等如何在社会的演绎中一步步隐喻化，从“仅仅是身体的一种病”转换成了一种道德批判，并进而转换成一种政治压迫的过程。文章最初连载于《纽约书评》，由于反响巨大，此后数年中两篇文章被多次集结成册出版，成为了社会批判的经典之作。","ebook_price":"14.99","series":{"id":"23686","title":"中英双语版桑塔格文集"},"price":"48.00"},"book_id":"25833473","id":1015320497},{"status":"read","comment":"啊，从此，我成了这个世界的囚犯……谁又能自我标榜有节操呢……翻译的好出戏啊……","updated":"2016-02-25 17:23:51","user_id":"2274326","rating":{"max":5,"value":"4","min":0},"book":{"rating":{"max":10,"numRaters":751,"average":"8.6","min":0},"subtitle":"","author":["[西]胡安·卡纳莱斯（Juan Díaz Canales） 文","胡安霍·瓜尔尼多（Juanjo Guarnido） 图"],"pubdate":"2015-6","tags":[{"count":509,"name":"漫画","title":"漫画"},{"count":314,"name":"黑猫侦探","title":"黑猫侦探"},{"count":210,"name":"欧漫","title":"欧漫"},{"count":157,"name":"绘本","title":"绘本"},{"count":128,"name":"西班牙","title":"西班牙"},{"count":112,"name":"推理","title":"推理"},{"count":85,"name":"胡安霍·瓜尔尼多","title":"胡安霍·瓜尔尼多"},{"count":81,"name":"法国漫画","title":"法国漫画"}],"origin_title":"Blacksad : Quelque part entre les ombres","image":"https://img1.doubanio.com\/mpic\/s28059508.jpg","binding":"精装","translator":["赵心舒"],"catalog":"","pages":"56","images":{"small":"https://img1.doubanio.com\/spic\/s28059508.jpg","large":"https://img1.doubanio.com\/lpic\/s28059508.jpg","medium":"https://img1.doubanio.com\/mpic\/s28059508.jpg"},"alt":"https:\/\/book.douban.com\/subject\/26369210\/","id":"26369210","publisher":"北京联合出版公司·后浪出版公司","isbn10":"7550250413